In order to use a serial mouse, you must tell the installation program which
serial port your mouse is connected to.  You must also indicate the number 
of buttons on your mouse.  If you are using a Mouse Systems Corporaton (MSC) 
compatible mouse, you must select Mouse Systems.  See the help facility or
the Installation Guide for more information.

Enter the following information about your serial mouse.
